Package com.netflix.zeno.genericobject

Class Summary
DiffHtmlCollectionLocker This class will line up two collections so that the most similar items are paired together.

This helps to eyeball the differences between two objects with collections in their hierarchies, without requiring knowledge of the semantics of these objects.

The similarity metric used here is the jaccard distance.
DiffHtmlGenerator This class generates HTML describing the differences between two GenericObjects.
GenericObject The GenericObject representation is used by the diff HTML generator.
GenericObject.Field  
GenericObjectFrameworkSerializer The GenericObject representation is used by the diff HTML generator.
GenericObjectSerializationFramework This framework is used to create a GenericObject representation of data.
JaccardMatrixPairwiseMatcher This class pulls out matches pairs of objects based on maximum jaccard similarity.

For a good discussion of how jaccard similarity matrix works, see http://matpalm.com/resemblance/jaccard_distance/
